snippet.title: Bionicle: Quest for Mata Nui - Trailer (Fan Made Open-World RPG Game)
snippet.description:
Bionicle: Quest for Mata Nui is a free fan made open-world RPG game that is set in the universe of Lego Bionicle. The project has been in development for the last six years and Im excited to finally reveal it.

Set during the first year of Bionicle, it follows the story of the Toa on their quest to collect the 6 great masks of power to rid the island of Mata Nui of the evil influence called Makuta.

Join our discord server for more info and regular updates!
https://discord.gg/jTfxtbD

-
